      "description": "The AllianzIM U.S. Equity 6 Month Buffer10 Jan/Jul ETF (SIXJ) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in downside hedge alternatives. The fund aims for specific buffered losses and capped gains on the SPDR S&P 500 ETF Trust over a specific holdings period. The actively-managed fund holds options and collateral. SIXJ was launched on Dec 31, 2021 and is issued by Allianz.",
